Interface ColumnWidthSaveable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlacementsHolderLocationsTableModel, PlacementsHolderPlacementsTableModel, PlacementsHolderTableModel
    public interface ColumnWidthSaveable
    An interface for TableModels that define how corresponding columns of the Table should be saved and restored
